    public class ORMRolemodelXYLayoutPolicy
extends ORMAbstractXYLayoutPolicy
    This XYLayoutEditPolicy handels request for creation and boundarie changes of all kinds Nodes in a Rolemodel and returns and creates the nessecary commands for the creation and boundarie change.
